items.description: 本项目是一个基于Spring Boot的电商平台，集成了商品展示、用户管理、购物车、订单管理、支付宝沙箱支付以及AI客服(deepseek部署)等功能。项目采用前后端分离架构，后端提供RESTful API接口，前端通过HTTP请求与后端交互，其余三端见首页仓库。

items.name: calc-v1-protocol-suite
items.description: calc-v1-protocol-suite is a TCP-based implementation of the CALC v1 custom binary protocol for a client-server calculator. It includes a binary protocol with metadata, Python server and client applications for arithmetic operations, a Lua Wireshark plugin for protocol analysis, and an RFC-style documentation (`RFC.md`).
